{"type":"message","id":"54cf1657","parentId":"e05331b9","timestamp":"2026-04-10T07:24:04.068Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The usage shows 5h 95% left - that means there's still 95% of the hourly quota remaining. If there was a rate limit, it would typically show in the session status or in the error messages. The fact that it says 95% left suggests the quota is not exhausted.\n\nWait, it says \"5h 95% left\" which could mean:\n- 95% of the hourly limit is remaining\n- Or 5 hours worth of usage is remaining at 95%\n\nLet me think about this - if there was a rate limit, the system would likely show an error. The session status looks normal. Let me explain this to the user."},{"type":"text","text":"从当前状态看，**没有看到限流迹象**：\n\n- 模型：`minimax/MiniMax-M2.7` 正常\n- 额度：`5h 95% left` — 本小时额度还剩 95%\n\n如果你的请求确实被限流了，可能原因：\n1. **触发频率限制** — 短时间内请求过于频繁\n2. **API 端问题** — MiniMax 侧临时抖动\n3. **并发超限** — 同一个 key 被多处使用\n\n遇到具体报错信息了吗？可以把错误截图或文字发给我，我帮你判断。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775805833068,"responseId":"0627d8898337b95329611aeaa3291197"}}
