{"type":"message","id":"a897898b","parentId":"b7ec5212","timestamp":"2026-04-10T07:24:36.496Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-10 15:24:34 GMT+8] Feishu[tts] DM | ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68 [msg:om_x100b52be15d488b0c2e7cbbabdaa3ee]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b52be15d488b0c2e7cbbabdaa3ee\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-04-10 15:24 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\"\n}\n```\n\n先做一个调试，使用vibesurf skill 驱动浏览器  打开百度，我看一下，咱们调试一下工具"}],"timestamp":1775805876491}}
